{
  "stem": "26983.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But later on-- and if you want, I can speak about it now-- the policy of the German together with Jakob Edelstein, who was the eldest of the Jews in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was also the representative of the Jewish community of Czechoslovakia-- of the [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Judenamt-- ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He came originally from, I think, a little village in Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he worked in Prague, and he was a great Zionist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And later on, he was the leader of the Jewish community of this Palastina-Amt.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he came with the first group of Jews who built up Theresienstadt in '41 with the AK transport, Arbeitskommando 1 and 2.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And his idea was that if we can persuade the German that here there will be a Jewish kind of ghetto which will help the German, and will help in a way us, and we will have better possibility to survive.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the German had their ideas.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They also needed, as we know today, a kind of cover for the pressure of the International Red Cross, who asked, where are the Jews?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What about these rumors?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they created a town, Theresienstadt, which was good at that time for both policy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The German thought about the possibility about showing this kind of ghetto-- the show-off ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Good conditions.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Edelstein-- his idea was to use it, or to persuade the Germans to-- that they should give something-- a place where the Jews can be creating for the German and can have all kinds of little factories, and help the Germans.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this idea was good for both.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And therefore, the Theresienstadt ghetto was created.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I'm a little child.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything was very well organized from the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They prepared us.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
